6 0 obj
<< /Length 1087 >>
stream
BT
/F1 10 Tf
50 785 Td
14 TL
(    for each k from 0 to N-2:) Tj
T*
(        old_r0 = red_final[k]) Tj
T*
(        new_r0 = red_final[k + 1]) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(        if new_r0 >= rule_base_range_TH:) Tj
T*
(            red_final[k + 1] = old_r0) Tj
T*
(            mark point k + 1 as rule01 affected) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Brief explanation:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  - If the next processed value is greater than or equal to rule_base_range_TH, it is) Tj
T*
(  treated as untrusted.) Tj
T*
(  - The viewer keeps the previous processed value instead of accepting the high value.) Tj
T*
(  - Green dots show where this rule changed the red curve.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Processing Order) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(raw r0) Tj
T*
(  -> deglitch function) Tj
T*
(  -> red_base) Tj
T*
(  -> optional rule01) Tj
T*
(  -> final red curve) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Current Defaults) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(median_win          = 9) Tj
T*
(spike_TH            = 0.065 m) Tj
T*
(jump_TH             = 0.253 m) Tj
T*
(rule_base_range_TH  = 1.1 m) Tj
T*
(rule01              = off by default) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Page 3 of 3) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
